data.name: BestPriceDescription
data.value: aracvararac.com's Call Your Own Price feature is unique in that it allows you to directly negotiate with the hotels for your nightly rate. All hotels, whether they be 5 star international brands or simple B&Bs with 5 rooms, wish for a 100% occupancy rate. At aracvararac.com, we act as intermiedaries between hotels who wish to fulfil this objective and our customers who are seeking for the lowest prices available, by getting a daily rate list of their unoccupied rooms from the hotels we work with. Hotels, wary of their reputations, do not advertise those special prices publicly. If and when your propsed rate is accepted by one or more of our member hotels, you receive a notification bearing the hotel's name and details. With aracvararac.com's Call Your Own Price, you get the lowest rate not available anywhere else.

data.name: DepositText
data.value: Supplier will require a deposit of TRY 500.0 at the time of receipt. It is a guarantee blocked on the credit card in case the vehicle is damaged or stolen. This will be released automatically if there is no theft or damage during the rental period.

data.name: ExemptionText
data.value: The vehicle has a damage exemption of EUR 500.0 (Tax Included) and a theft exemption of EUR 500.0 (Including Tax). When you receive the vehicle, please make sure that there is an exemption amount on your card.

data.name: InsuranceCoverageText
data.value: Damage Liability (CASCO) Insurance (CDW): 18% Tax Included; Wide Coverage 500 EUR

data.name: InsuranceCoverageText2
data.value: Complete scope package: 50 TRY daily 18% Tax Included

data.name: InsuranceCoverageText3
data.value: Theft protection: 18% Tax Included; Wide Coverage 500 EUR

data.name: InsuranceCoverageText5
data.value: The Exemption Obligation is the maximum amount determined by your car rental supplier, where you can be held liable in case the vehicle is damaged / stolen. Damage or loss to tires, windshields, glass or chassis may not be covered by CDW (Disclaimer of Accident Damage). Please contact the rental agency at the office.

data.name: InsuranceCoverageText6
data.value: If you purchased Exemption Payment Insurance from a third party, the main driver must present the credit card at the rental office for the car rental agency to approve the deposit.

data.name: ToBeInformed

data.name: ToBeInformedText
data.value: Customers can opt out at any time.

data.name: AdditionalDriverText
data.value: Additional drivers can be added to your rental for a fee of 7 EUR per day Maximum 105 EUR 18% Tax Included. When you pick up your car, please pay for additional drivers at the rental office.

data.name: BestPricesText
data.value: We find you the best prices in the market

data.name: CancellationText1
data.value: What is your cancellation policy for full prepaid or partial payments? 1 - If you cancel the vehicle up to 48 hours before you receive it, the full amount will be refunded to you. 2 - If you cancel less than 48 hours before receiving, you will receive a refund after deducting TRY388. If your online payment is less than TRY388, no refund will be given for your car rental reservation. 3 - If your reservation is made less than 48 hours before receiving the car, the cancellation policy will be automatically applied to your reservation. 4 - All cancellations must be made through our online portal, not through the car rental agency. If you agree to cancel directly with the car rental agency on arrival, you must also inform us about this change regarding your reservation. 5 - It may not be possible to change your reservation or cancel optional extras in less than 48 hours before receiving the vehicle. If you purchased our Damage Return Insurance product and then decided to cancel your rental car reservation, Damage Return Insurance will be canceled automatically. If you want to change or rearrange your reservation, the Damage Return Insurance will be canceled at the beginning. However, we will automatically create a new policy for your new reservation. In either case, you will receive an e-mail sent to your e-mail address provided during the online booking process to confirm the cancellation. Please note that if you cancel your insurance policy in less than 24 hours after the start of your car rental agreement, no refund will be made for your insurance. What is my reservation? The 'failure to use a reservation' is for the following reasons: 1 - You did not inform us about your cancellation before your checkout time. 2 - You could not receive the vehicle at the specified time and date. 3 - You could not provide the necessary documentation to receive the vehicle.4 - You could not provide a credit card issued on behalf of the main driver with sufficient balance. No refunds will be given to you in any of the above. The car rental company reserves the right to refuse to provide a vehicle if you do not arrive on time with a sufficient credit card for all the necessary documentation and the deposit of the vehicle. In this case, you will not be entitled to a refund if the car rental has not been canceled at least 48 hours ago.

data.name: DepositAndCreditCardInformationText1
data.value: IT IS ACCEPTED American Express, Diners Club, MasterCard (no debit or prepaid card), Visa (not prepaid). Unless otherwise stated below, debit cards are not accepted.

data.name: DepositAndCreditCardInformationText2
data.value: A deposit of minimum EUR 200.0 to maximum EUR 600.0 will be retained on your credit card for the duration of the lease. Your deposit is a guarantee kept in case of damage / theft. This amount will be released automatically if there is no theft or damage during the rental period. Note that this does not represent your total exemption liability, which can be found in your Insurance Coverage section.

data.name: DepositAndCreditCardInformationText3
data.value: You will need to pass the Findeks credit score assessment by the rental agency. If you fail this assessment, the car rental agency may not deliver the vehicle. In these cases, the amounts paid will not be refunded. To check your credit rating, please visit www.findeks.com or contact the rental office by phone.

data.name: DepositAndCreditCardInformationText4
data.value: THESE ARE NOT ACCEPTED: No other form of payment will be accepted.

data.name: DepositAndCreditCardInformationText5
data.value: A valid credit card on behalf of the main driver must be presented at the rental office to pre-authorize / charge a deposit. The credit card (s) must be embossed and a PIN number may be required.

data.name: DepositAndCreditCardInformationText6
data.value: The car rental agency may not deliver the vehicle if you are unable to offer a valid credit card or if your credit card does not have sufficient funds or if the credit card is not on behalf of the original driver. In these cases, the amounts paid will not be refunded.

data.name: DriverLicenseText1
data.value: Full driver's license for at least 1 year with no major traffic violations record. UK driving license holders must present their photo cards.

data.name: DriverLicenseText2
data.value: If your driver's license is not written in Latin alphabet (for example, Arabic, Greek, Russian or Chinese) you will need to bring in an International Driver's License and your local driver's license. For driver licenses from countries that are not part of your international driver's license, an official translation of the document must be accompanied by an original document. When hired within the EU, customers from non-EU countries must present an International Driving License along with their local documents.

data.name: DriverYearsOldText1
data.value: Customers outside the age restrictions will not be able to rent a car unless there is a young or old driver's fee specified in this section. Please note that, if applicable, this fee will be included in the rental price and will be paid in local currency at the rental office upon arrival.

data.name: ExtrasText
data.value: All extras are paid at the car rental provider's office upon receipt. Note that the availability of these extras is not always guaranteed and prices are subject to change. In most countries, child car seats are compulsory for children 12 years old or under 135 cm tall.

data.name: FeesText1
data.value: Please note that credit card fees apply. Fees vary by card type, please consult the supplier at the office.

data.name: FuelPolicyText2
data.value: Your vehicle will be delivered to you with a full tank. To avoid paying fuel costs, you must deliver the vehicle with a full tank. When you deliver the vehicle with the tank full, you may need to provide a fuel deposit on your credit card to be canceled or returned. The missing fuel will be charged when you deliver the vehicle. The liter fuel charge received by the rental agency may be significantly higher than the price at the local gas station. Refueling fees may also apply.

data.name: FuelPolicyText3
data.value: Unless otherwise stated in the price information, fuel fees can be paid at the rental office.

data.name: IdentitiesText
data.value: A valid photo ID (Passport or Identity Card).

data.name: KilometersPolicyText3
data.value: Number of kilometers to be rented: 400

data.name: OptionalExtraTermsText1
data.value: Please note the following: The price of optional extras is subject to change without notice. Optional extras are subject to availability. Changes made in the office may be subject to local surcharges.

data.name: ReceiptText1
data.value: On arrival, your confirmation document must be printed in the rental office. Failure to show the certification indicates that the rental agency may charge local prices. Please note: We are not responsible for excessive pricing that may be applied to the rental if the certification cannot be shown at the local agency during vehicle delivery. If you cannot show the required documents, if the documents are not valid or if your credit card does not have sufficient funds, the car rental agent may refuse to deliver the vehicle and no fee will be refunded.
